Date: 1994-05-16

Title: BRST Structures and Symplectic Geometry on a Class of Supermanifolds

Authors: Sergio Albeverio and Shao-Ming Fei

Comments: 14 pages, Latex

Journal-ref: Lett.Math.Phys. 33 (1995) 207-219

By investigating the symplectic geometry and geometric quantization on aclass of supermanifolds, we exhibit BRST structures for a certain kind ofalgebras. We discuss the undeformed and q-deformed cases in the classical aswell as in the quantum cases.